<table width=75%>
<tr><td bgcolor="#0000AF">
<strong><font color=white>
<center>Mystic Cloak Quest</center>
</font></strong>
</td></tr>
</table><BR>
<div align="left">
1) Head to Najena and in one of the jail cells is a NPC named Linara Parlone.  Talk to her to get the quest.<BR>
<BR>
2) Head to Unrest and kill The Priest of Najena.  He is on the 3rd Floor.  He will drop a key.<BR>
<BR>
3) Head back to Najena and give the key to Linara.  She will give you a note to give to her father.<BR>
<BR>
4) Head to Felwithe and find her father.  Give him the note and he will give you a worn cloak.<BR>
<BR>
5) Head to Erudin and into the Enchanters' Guild.  Find the mother of Linara and give her the cloak.  You will receive the Mystic Cloak in return.<BR>
</div>
<BR>
