<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>HA!! I am back, now I have completed this quest along with a friend of mine and would like to make a few comments about it.  I was lucky enough to hear someone /OOC "Priest Up" at that time I was in teh Torture Room in the basement and I bolted to his spawn on the SECOND FLOOR.  I grabbed him then trained him to my group and we beat the smack outta him then I got my Key.  <BR>
<BR>
My friend Jakye however was not so lucky to stumble upon him and had to camp him for about 12 hours.  The Priest of Najena has a Place Holder of a normal Ghoul that spawns about every 54 minutes, it has been my expirience while fighting in Unrest that the Priest will spawn once out of every 10-15 spawns.  However most people camp him till they get the Key so if you find the spawn open, prepare to spend some time there.<BR>
<BR>
The priest of Najena conned White to me at level 31 and does some pretty wicked spell casting to if you are not 36+ get some friends in the general area to back you up.  Plus the area you must fight him in is a tight plavce not suited for any caster of Damage spells, it is almost smart to run him outside and gang jump him.  WARNING!!  If you do massive dmg to this enemy quickly he will run straight to the basement to get friends that will be very pissed, you haev been warned. <BR>
<BR>
The rest of the quest is easy, follow the directions.  If you have any questions email me at Wrath_of_the_magi@hotmail.com</font></td></tr></table>
