<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Question answers:<BR>
<BR>
1#  Unrest is located On faydwer, from Gfay go to Butcher Block then follow the left wall in BB.  This will lead you to Dagnors Cauldron, In dagnors, it is on the right side of the lake, but it helps to get a loc on the cave that enters the estate of Unrest.  <BR>
<BR>
2#  This quest can be completed solo at about level 33-35 or so, any lower and I would seriously suggest a back up person next to you.  The quest can easily be done by 2 level 29s or 30s of just about any class.  <BR>
<BR>
3# The name of the key the priest drops is the Tarnished Bronze Key.</font></td></tr></table>
